- **CVSS:** [Score]
- **Description:** [Short description]
- **Impact:** [What an attacker can do]
- **Fix:** Update to [version] or later
- **Location:** `package.json` / `Cargo.toml` / etc.

[...repeat...]

## Version Freshness
